text: Cliburn is a village and civil parish in Eden, Cumbria, England. In 2001 there were 204 people living in Cliburn. It has a church called St Cuthbert's Church. == References == == Other websites == * http://www.thecumbriadirectory.com/Town_or_Village/location.php?url=cliburn Category:Villages in Cumbria Category:Civil parishes in Cumbria
